quran[86]{c,v,t}:
  78,1,Vanobvunzana maererano nei
  78,2,"Maererano nenhaurwa huru (Islaam, Qur’aan iri uye Zuva Rekutongwa)"
  78,3,Pamusoro payo vanopokana
  78,4,"Hongu, vachazviziva"
  78,5,"Hongu, vachazviziva zvekare"
  78,6,Hatina here kusika pasi semubhedha
  78,7,Uye makomo sehoko
  78,8,"Zvakare tikave tinokusikai muri vaviri vaviri (murume nemukadzi, akareba neakapfupika, akanaka neakaipa)"
  78,9,Uye tikava tinokupai hope kuti muve munozorora
  78,10,Uye tikave tinosika usiku sehwidibiro
  78,11,Uye takasika masikati kuti muwane raramo
  78,12,Tikava tinovaka pamusoro penyu matenga manomwe
  78,13,Uye tikasika mwenje unopenya (zuva)
  78,14,Uye tikatumira mvura zhinji kubva kumakore
  78,15,Kuti tive tinoburitsa zvirimwa
  78,16,Uye nemapindu ezvirimwa zvakabatana zvakasvibira
  78,17,"Zvirokwazvo, zuva remutongo inguva yakatarwa"
  78,18,"Zuva iro richaridzwa hwamanda, uye muchauya muri muzvikwata"
  78,19,Uye matenga achavhurwa oita segonhi
  78,20,Uye makomo achabviswa munzvimbo dzawo sezvinonzi aiva madzimudzangara
  78,21,"Zvirokwazvo, Gehena inzvimbo yakaipa"
  78,22,Nzvimbo ichapindwa neavo vanotyora mirawo yaAllah
  78,23,Vachapindamo zvachose
  78,24,"Hapana kana chinwiwa chichange chichitonhorera chavachamwa imomo, kana chinwiwa chipi zvacho"
  78,25,"Kusara kwemvura yakwatiswa, uye nezvose zvakaipa zvinobuda pamuviri"
  78,26,Mubairo unoenderana nezvavaiita
  78,27,"Zvirokwazvo, vakange vasingambotarisiri kuzotongwa"
  78,28,Uye vakaramba zviratidzo zvedu zvachose
  78,29,Uye zvinhu zvose takave tinozvinyora muGwaro
  78,30,Saka chiravirai (magumo emabasa enyu akaipa). Hatisi kuzokuwedzerai kusara kwemarwadzo
  78,31,"Muzvokwadi, kune avo vanotya Allah kuchange kune budiriro (Paradhiso)"
  78,32,Yemapindu nemagirepi
  78,33,Uye mhandara dzezera rimwe dzakanaka
  78,34,Uye komichi izere newaini
  78,35,Havambonzwi imomo nhaurwa dzakaipa kana manyepo
  78,36,"Mubairo kubva kuna Tenzi vako, chipo chakaverengwa (chinoenderana nezvakanaka zvavaiita)"
  78,37,"Kubva kuna Tenzi vematenga nepasi rino uye zvose zviri mukati mavo, vane ngoni zhinji, avo vasingakwanise kutaura navo (kunze kwekuti vavapa mvumo)"
  78,38,"Pazuva iro Ar-Rooh (Gabriel kana imwe ngirozi) nengirozi dzichange dzakamira mumitsara, hapana achataura kana nani kusara kweuyo Allah vavanopa mvumo, uye achitaura zvinhu zvakanaka"
  78,39,"(Pasina kana kusagutsikana) Iri ndiro zuva rechokwadi. Saka, uyo anoda ngaave anotsvaga nzvimbo yakanaka (kana nzira yakanaka ye) kuna Tenzi vake (nekuvateerera pasi rino)"
  78,40,"Zvirokwazvo, takakuyambirai pamusoro pemarwadzo epadyo epazuva iro munhu wese achange achiona zvose zvakatungamidzwa nemaoko ake (zvaaita), uye uyo akange asingatendi achati: “Ndinokungura kuti ndingadai ndaiva ivhu.”"
  79,1,Ndinopika neidzo (ngirozi) dzinotora (upenyu hweuyo asingatendi) nechisimba
  79,2,Neidzo (ngirozi) dzinobvisa zvinyoro-nyoro (mweya wevatendi)
  79,3,Uye neidzo dzinopeperuka
  79,4,Uye neidzo dzinoenderera mberi nekumhanyidzana (ngirozi kana nyenyedzi kana mabhiza)
  79,5,"Uye idzo (ngirozi) dzinoronga kutevedzera mirairo yaTenzi vadzo, (saka zvirokwazvo imi vasingatendi muchabvunzwa)"
  79,6,"Pazuva iro pasi rino nemakomo paachandengendeka zvakanyanya (uye wese achafa, hwamanda yekutanga yaridzwa)"
  79,7,Hwamanda yepiri paichaitevera (uye wese achamutswa)
  79,8,(Mimwe) moyo zuva racho ichandengendeka nekutya
  79,9,Maziso avo achange akatsikitsira
  79,10,"Vanoti: “Tichadzoserwa zvirokwazvo here pahupenyu hwedu hwekare?”"
  79,11,“Mushure mekunge tava mabhonzo akatsetseka?”
  79,12,"Vanoti: “Nokudaro kuchava kudzokera kwekurasikirwa!”"
  79,13,"Asi zvirokwazvo icharidzwa (hwamanda) kamwechete (kuridzwa kechipiri, Surah)"
  79,14,Apo vachazoona vava pamusoro pevhu (vari vapenyu mushure mekufa)
  79,15,Hakuna here kuuya nhaurwa yaMusa kwauri
  79,16,Apo Tenzi vake vakamushevedza munzvimbo inoera yeTuwaa
  79,17,"(Vakati kwaari): “Enda kuna Farawo, zvirokwazvo arikufurikidza mwero (nekusatenda nekuita zvakaipa).”"
  79,18,"Omutaurira kuti: “Ungazvichenure here (kubva mukusatenda)?”"
  79,19,"“Uye kuti ndive ndinokutungamira kuna Tenzi vako, kuti uve unovatya?”"
  79,20,Uye Musa akamuratidza chiratidzo chihombe
  79,21,Asi (Farawo) akaramba uye haana kuteerera
  79,22,"Uye akapfuratira, akashingirira (achipokana naAllah)"
  79,23,Uye akaunganidza (vanhu vake) ndokushevedzera
  79,24,"Achiti: “Ndini Tenzi venyu mukuru”"
  79,25,Saka Allah vakamukweva nemutongo wekubva kwekutanga nekupedzisira kwekuraudzira kwake
  79,26,"Zvirokwazvo, mune izvi mune chidzidzo kune uyo anotya Allah"
  79,27,Munonetsa kusika here kana kuti denga ravakagadzira
  79,28,Vakarisimudza vakarinatsurudza
  79,29,Husiku hwaro vakaufukidza nerima uye vakaburitsamo chiedza
  79,30,Uye mushure mezvo ndokubva vawaridza nyika
  79,31,Vakaunza kubvamo mvura uye nemafuro
  79,32,Uye nemakomo vakaiisa zvakasimba
  79,33,(Kuitira kuti) mubatsirikane nekudya kwenyu nemombe dzenyu
  79,34,Asi kana kukauya dambudziko guru (zuva rekutongwa)
  79,35,Zuva iro munhu acharangarira zvaaiita
  79,36,Uye moto weGehena uchava pachena kune (wese) anoona
  79,37,Kune uyo aityora mitemo yese (nekusatenda nekusateerera Allah)
  79,38,Uye akasarudza upenyu hwepasi pano (achiita zvido zvake)
  79,39,"Zvirokwazvo, Gehena ndiyo nzvimbo (yake) yokugara"
  79,40,"Asi uyo aitya kumira pamberi paTenzi vake, uye akazvidzora kubva kuhuipi hwakasviba uye nemakaro"
  79,41,"Zvirokwazvo, Paradhiso ndokwaachagara"
  79,42,"Vanokubvunza (Muhammad (SAW)) pamusoro penguva yekutongwa, kuti zuva racho ndirinhi"
  79,43,Hauna ruzivo kutaura chimwe chinhu pamusoro payo
  79,44,Kuna Tenzi vako ndiko kune ruzivo rwenguva yacho
  79,45,Zvirokwazvo iwe (Muhammad (SAW)) uri muyambiri kune avo vanoritya
  79,46,Zuva ravachaiona kuchava sekunge havana kugara (pano panyika) kusiya kwemasikati kana mangwanani